EI: 是\\
南农高质量: A\\
TLDR: An unsupervised object-oriented change detection approach empowered by hierarchical multi-scale segmentation for generating binary ecosystem change maps and leverages multidimensional features to adapt the Iteratively Reweighted Multivariate Alteration Detection (IRMAD) algorithm for GaoFen WFV data is proposed.},
